name: Kangatel
overview:
Kangatel offers call-by-call service to reduce the cost of international calls.

Users just type a short 6 digit code for example ‘29 03 57’ to call countries like Australia, New Zealand, Poland, Germany and many other countries, and then dial their destination number. That really is it!

* billed by the second not the minute
* all calls are deducted from regular phone credits
* no registration, no pre-payments and no accounts
* no connection fees, no topup fees
* easy 6 digit codes not long numbers when you call from a mobile
* international calls without ANY hidden fees
* no need to worry about how long your credit lasts
* avoid expensive 0844 / 0845 / 0906 numbers when using your mobile
* no international calling cards necessary
* works with T-Mobile and 3-Mobile contract and Pay As You Go
* works with Orange PaynGo

external_links.title: Kangatel's call-by-call service is cheaper than Skype
